'Aleksei Valentinovich Vanyushin' (; born January 3, 1982 in Orekhovo-Zuyevo)
is a Russian professional footballer. Currently, he plays for FC Znamya Truda
Orekhovo-Zuyevo .

He played for the main squad of FC Krylia Sovetov Samara in the Russian Premier
League Cup.
